A simple app for adding anonymous and signed in feedback to a site.

Features:
* Using the templatetag the feedback tab can be added to the side of any page.
* If clicked a modular overlay (Facebox) is opened displaying the feedback
* The referring url, current url and user agent are also stored with the feedback.
* Feedback can be categorized
* There is a very simple backend. Moderators can close, open and assign tickets.

Dependencies:
Facebox (http://chriswanstrath.com/facebox/)
Templated-Emails (https://github.com/philippWassibauer/templated-emails)